  "description": "Use when re-assigning record OwnerId across many records \u2014 territory realignment, employee departure, region split, integration cleanup. Triggers: 'mass transfer accounts', 'reassign opportunities to new owner', 'transfer all records on user deactivation', 'OwnerId migration'. NOT for assignment rules, queue routing, or single-record manual transfer.",
